videos.description: Villanova freshman Saddiq Bey runs a pick-and-roll and finds Dhamir Cosby-Roundtree for a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Villanova pick-and-roll leads to slam

videos.description: Shizz Alston Jr. pokes it away and puts down a one-handed dunk at the other end for Temple.
videos.headline: Temple's Alston steals and dunks

videos.headline: Villanova's Paschall flashes post moves for dunk
